{
  "texts": [
    "For AI-based ML models to be a successful strategic resource, they must include transparency (Raisch & Krakowski, 2021), allowing decision-makers to use AI's analytical and computational capabilities to support and drive data-centric decision-making.",
    "By creating an implementation framework which incorporates explainability components in AI-based systems, we can advance the field of AI.",
    "Such a framework in the financial sector will make it easier for managers to comprehend the reasoning behind decisions the AI systems suggest.",
    "AI applications must be transparent and understandable now and in the future to Fig. 3 The research onion (Source: Saunders et al., 2007) supplement and support human intellect in taking decisions.",
    "This will promote ethical and responsible AI use in businesses (Brock & Von Wangenheim, 2019; Shrestha et al., 2021)."
  ]
}